&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://azeizle.tistory.com/entry/2017-malibu-vs-2016-pasat-rival-test-driving-in-korea&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;- [비교시승] 올 뉴 말리부 vs 파사트 계급장 떼고 붙어 보면?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://azeizle.tistory.com/entry/9gen-all-new-malibu-test-drive-in-korea&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;- [시승기] 올 뉴 말리부 경쟁력을 확인해 보다&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://azeizle.tistory.com/entry/9gen-chevolet-malibu-test-drive-in-korea&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;- [시승기] 올 뉴 말리부 국산 중형세단 올킬의 신호탄?!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://azeizle.tistory.com/entry/renault-samsung-SM3-diesel-test-drive-in-korea&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;- [시승기] SM3 디젤 디자인만 변한다면~&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://azeizle.tistory.com/entry/Renault-samsung-SM6-GDe-test-drive-performance-ridign&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;- [시승기] SM6 GDe 편안함의 매력 속에서 즐거움 찾기&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://azeizle.tistory.com/entry/Renault-samsung-full-change-SM6-TCE-test-drive&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;- [시승기] SM6 TCE 1.6 터보의 즐거움을 끌어내다&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span&gt;
